      },
      "date": "2017-04-19 16:52:44.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nTests uploaded by Trevis Autotest from trevis-8vm5 for review-zfs-part-2 received by maloo, run on CentOS Linux 7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/bc007300-d32c-4840-8342-db3363d83dae). Ran 10 tests. No failures.",
